    <div class="methodology-note">
      All comparison systems received a schema-aware wrapper granting them pin-status filtering, open-question routing, and scope isolation for free at evaluation time. Competitors fail purely on retrieval precision — the structural routing logic was given to them. Results reflect pinned Docker image digests. <a href="https://github.com/tenurehq/precisionMemBench" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reproduce locally →</a>
